{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20629, "create_time": 1641184908, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "养了多少尸位素餐的官僚公务员？\n平时你老百姓打各种政府热线不是占线就是没人接就是踢皮球。\n平时你官僚舒服躺着领工资，到了疫情要你做事做得一塌糊涂。\n官僚只对乌纱帽负责。常说领导有决断力下层才有行动力。领导不需要亲自办事，只要对下级说“这件事能办你就办，不能办就换人办”。最后责任踢到基层，基层没有协调力就瞎办一通。", "timestamp": 1641184908}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20630, "create_time": 1641185255, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "这套层层隶属的庞杂官僚体系养了一堆土皇帝养了一堆黑社会。可能也许上面觉得只有土皇帝才能管得住基层吧", "timestamp": 1641185255}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20631, "create_time": 1641185270, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 1, "text": "[tmp]\n总比美国死几十万人强", "timestamp": 1641185270}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20633, "create_time": 1641185459, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 疫情清零是谁的功劳值得探讨，是官僚体系高效运作呢还是人民守秩序像家畜一样温顺", "timestamp": 1641185459}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20635, "create_time": 1641185656, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "可防可控的不是病毒，而是人民", "timestamp": 1641185656}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20636, "create_time": 1641185858, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re 洞主: 官僚体系不运作的话，人民想守秩序都不知道怎么守", "timestamp": 1641185858}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 20639, "create_time": 1641186218, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 隔离这有啥难的，挥挥鞭子人民就温顺自觉地把自己关在家里，再运送些食物不致饿死就行了。需要养那么多官员吗，颐使气指的领导爷，丑态百出的执行人"